column5: Anyone know of any sites or places where i can get free topograph images of lakes? im having a hard time finding out information on a fee places including lang lake.
Topo is on line here.  http://atlas.nrcan.gc.ca/site/english/maps/topo/map  Depth maps I am not sure....  Usually you have to pay or sometime the MNR has them.  Cheers
Search anglers atlas,, they have a ton of free maps to download, i have done pretty good with them on places i have been ,,, you need to register for free also,, good luck
